N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 166-2.1 - Purpose

State Regulations

The purpose of this Subpart is to set forth regulations and
procedures governing the availability of records of the Division for Youth, pursuant to the provisions of article 6 of the Public Officers Law, known as
the Freedom of Information Law. Notes
